sections.heading: 37-1001 to 37-1008 shall be known and may be cited as the Trail Development Assistance Act
sections.text: The Trail Development Assistance Act shall terminate January 1, 2010, and any money in the Trail Development Assistance Fund at such time shall be transferred to the General Fund.
